                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950916-15-defend189 t17950916-15-punish78"></join>
               Privately Whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron THOMPSON.</p>
